Class SystemLoggerModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team5940.robot_core.modules.AbstractModule

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoggerModule, Module

    public class SystemLoggerModule
extends AbstractLoggerModule
    This is a simple logger that uses whatever the System's out and err are set to. They should show up in Riolog.
